Welcome to LittleGiraffePrints ❤ 
----------------------------------------------

This listing is a PHYSICAL PRINT SET of 3 which is printed on High-End Professional Photographic Paper. No Frame Included.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

BUY 2 and GET 40% OFF total price and
FREE WORLDWIDE DELIVERY

------------------------------------------------------

The Prints sizes available are A4, A5, 8x10 and 5x7 and 4x6 Inches or Emailed.

and can be printed on Matt, Satin, or Gloss. IF you can't decide I have listed the benefits of each.

Gloss — gloss coated paper has a high sheen. Gloss papers have less bulk and opacity and are typically less expensive than dull & matte paper of equal thickness. Gloss coatings reduce ink absorption, which give the sheet an excellent color definition.

Satin — a satin coating is a less shiny coated finish. It has a lower gloss level than gloss finish, yet a higher gloss level than matte finish. Colors are sharp and vivid.

Matte — a matte coated paper is a non-glossy, flat looking paper with very little sheen. Matte papers are more opaque, contain greater bulk, and are higher in cost. The coating still keeps much of the ink from being absorbed by the paper, which produces excellent, vibrant color.

results.title: Under the Drusy Moon, cobalt calcite drusy Pendant, Lemon Chacedony Pendant, Burnt Fire Agate Pendant, 3 pendant necklace, statement piece
results.description: This 3 piece pendant is definitely one-of-a-kind.  Cobalt Calcite Druzy (Pink), Lemon Chalcedony (yellow-green) and Fire agate (black and white), are each suspended on silver pendants from one 5" heavy silver wire, which is attached to silver rolo chain.  There are three words stamped into the backs of the pendants (one word per pendant), LIVE, LOVE, LAUGH.  the total length of the piece is 17.5 inches, and can be cinched up to the second ring, which is at 16".  Cobalt Calcite Druzy is truly a stunning and sparkling stone, and this one has a circumference of 1".  I make variations of this type of necklace, but no two are alike, as these stones cannot be found in bulk, but I carefully pick and chose these stones, which have been cut by lapidary artists.  As in so many of my pieces, the way this piece is designed is the pendants are all suspended together, but can move independent of each other, to create interest.

As we also sell this fabric in our retail shop, sometimes our inventory is off.  You can leave instructions for us including how you want the order shipped.   This helps avoid any delays that might happen by trying to contact you.  The choices are as follows:

ORDERED AMOUNT ONLY - Cancel the order if you do not have the stated amount in continuous yardage.
SEND WHAT YOU HAVE - Send the amount you have. We will adjust the prices and shipping accordingly.
CONTACT ME - If you do NOT have the exact amount, please contact me for instructions (the default for our shop).
SEE NOTE - Leave any instructions in the customers note section.

CHOOSE YOUR FABRIC LENGTH FROM THE FOLLOWING:
1/4 yards ( 9 inches x 44 inches)
FAT QUARTER (18 inches x 22 inches) 
1/2 yards (18 inches x 44 inches)
3/4 yards (27 inches x 44 inches)
1 yard (36 inches x 44 inches)
1 1/4 yards (45 inches x 44 inches)
1 1/2 yards (54 inches x 44 inches)

The quantity button will allow you to purchase 1/4 yard, 1/2 yard, 3/4 yard, 1 yard, 1-1/4 yard and 1-1/2 yard cuts. The price is listed next to the size in the drop down menu.   Multiple quantities will be cut in a single continuous piece unless otherwise stated.  Do not order more yardage than what is listed in the drop down box.

Example:  If you wish to purchase 3 yards, select the 1 yard cut from the drop down menu and then a quantity of 3.  You can purchase multiple lengths of the same fabric as long as it does not exceed the total quantity listed on the drop down menu.

Fabric cut sizes are approximate as the width of cotton fabrics vary between 43 and 45 inches.  Fabric is cut with a rotary cutter on a ruled mat to provide you with the straight cuts whenever possible.

If you need a custom listing for a length not listed or would like help in coordinating or calculating yardage for your projects, please convo us or request a custom listing via the custom order button at the top right of this page.  Sometimes we have more fabric in stock than what is listed.   If for some reason we have less fabric than shown, we will contact you for instructions unless otherwise instructed.  

Shipping is via first class mail for up to 2 yards. 3 to 8 yards ship via a priority flat rate envelope.   We use calculated shipping based on weight, and offer "FREE" domestic Priority Mail shipping on orders higher orders, this will be displayed when ordering..  Shipping upgrades and international rates are available at check-out.  If a significant overcharge in shipping happens due to a combined or multiple yard purchase, it will be refunded to you.   When buying multiple quantities of small fabric yardage shipping prices can be off and force priority mail prices before needed.   Please let us know if you wish first class shipping in this case.

We try to show multiple images of each fabric.  The first is usually from the Manufacturer or supplier.  The second displays a ruler so that you can get an idea of the size of the fabric design and pattern.  Others are usually close ups or project ideas.   NOTE:  Sometimes the pictures we take vary in color from the manufacturer's picture due to cameras, lighting and other factors.  In most cases, the first image will be the most accurate in displaying the true color(s).

results.title: Stackable Love Live Laugh Midi Rings, Stamped Adjustable Knuckle Rings. Set of Three Midi Rings,  Stamped Aluminum Midi Rings
results.description:
Love, Live, Laugh are words to live by!

This set of three stackable midi rings lets the world know how you feel.

This set of knuckle rings are approximately US size 3.5 but I can tailor them to fit whatever finger that you wish to wear them on.

A general rule of thumb is that a midi ring will be 3-4 sizes smaller than your normal size. For example, if you are a size 7 on your middle finger, you should take a size 4 in midi ring.

Midi rings are rings that sits on your finger above the lower knuckle. While the trend sounds limiting, there are actually a ton of ways to own this midi ring look! In this example, the model is wearing midi rings as her primary jewelry staple. We love how she has one on almost every finger to create a line effect.
